    "title": "אַחֵֽינוּ וְאַחֱיוֹתֵנוּ | Aḥeinu v'Aḥeiyoteinu, an inclusive adaptation of the prayer for captives after 7 October 2023 by Me’ira Rakhel Pitkapaasi",
